# Unreal Engine generated files
Binaries/
DerivedDataCache/
Intermediate/
Saved/

# Unreal Engine generated files inside plugins
# If a plugin is distributed as binary-only, remove the matching Binaries/ ignore rule for that plugin.
Plugins/**/Binaries/
Plugins/**/Intermediate/
Plugins/**/Saved/
Plugins/**/DerivedDataCache/
Plugins/**/mcp_output/
Plugins/**/.codebuddy/

